videos.headline: Wagner celebrates after winning NEC, punching ticket to Big Dance
videos.description: Wagner defeats Merrimack in the Northeast Conference title game to clinch a spot in the NCAA tournament for the first time since 2003.

videos.headline: Kicked ball accidentally hits ref directly in the face
videos.description: An unfortunate bounce off of a kicked inbounds pass ends up hitting a referee in the face during the NEC championship game.
